### CardAction : add_anim_action
``` lua
local card_action	-- example card_action
local on_anim_step	-- example function

card_action:add_anim_action( 3, on_anim_step )
```

Assigns a **`function`** to be executed when the <%= @link_character %> reaches a specific step in the animation.

_The step number is **not** equal to the amount of frames passed._<br>
_It increases by **`1`** every time the <%= @link_character %> changes state based upon the data in its `.animation` file._

#### Function Call
`card_action:add_anim_action( step_number, on_anim_step )`

#### Parameters
**`integer`** `step_number`<br>
	&emsp;_The **step number** you want to execute the **`function`** at._<br>
**`function`** `on_anim_step`<br>
	&emsp;_The **`function`** that will be executed when entering the specified animation step._<br>
